 Galvatron was bored. He still hadnt tested a quater of his new powers. He 
decided to check out and see what had happened to his old friend. He sent a 
comm to Hot Rod. "Hello my old friend meet me at the following corridinates. 
I wish that we test eachother a bit. I have missed you." he rocketed off to 
the coordinates he sent Hot Rod. It was in the middle of an open valley. Over 
somewhere in modern day sahera desert. It wasnt a desert yet. He flew with 
his dragon wings spread at top speed.
